<p>Should be contained within a <span class="script">XULElem("bindings")</span> element. A <code>binding</code> is used to bind a variable to a node. Like the <span class="script">XULElem("triple")</span> element in syntax, it can be used to bind a particular property of a matched node to a particular variable name. That name can then be used within the action of a rule.</p>
<dl> <dt>Properties</dt> <dd><span class="script">PrefAnch("p-", "object")</span>, <span class="script">PrefAnch("p-", "predicate")</span>, <span class="script">PrefAnch("p-", "subject")</span></dd>
</dl>
